{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"毛泽东的身影","authors":["于书恒"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":12,"day":25}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东的身影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于书恒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻开党史长卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻找伟人的足迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东的身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是那么清晰——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把雨伞，撑着风雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双草鞋，踏着崎岖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是农民的儿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熟习播种、扶犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于，在东方的地平线上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁出一个崭新的世纪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在苦难的民族心中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点燃了“井冈火炬”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你善于写作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是位大手笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总以国家的存亡命题。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雪愈浓，愈有激情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪声愈紧，愈添诗意；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在曲折中构思光明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在烽火中锤炼真理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撰写了古今中外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最长的一部巨著，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从江西到陕北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两万五千里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你与牧羊人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延河边相聚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只野果掰开尝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一杆烟袋轮着吸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个小“八路”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝塔山下缠着你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没讲完的故事接着讲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"末了，问小米饭香不香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想家的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可曾哭过鼻子？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两朵山丹丹，笑开在圣地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门城楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一挥手臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把东方“睡狮”唤起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此，一个受欺凌的民族，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在全世界面前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把腰杆挺直，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像天安门广场的五星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥展风雨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，毛泽东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的好主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年你站着的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是中流砥柱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今你卧下来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是坚牢的基石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那上面飘扬的五星红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不正是你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在向人民招手致意！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}